OL,3,CHome Office to pay TikTok influencers
OL,4,Cto deter migrants from crossing Channel
OL,6,F"People smugglers frequently use
OL,7,Fsocial media to peddle lies and
OL,8,Fpromote their criminal activities, and
OL,9,Fit is vital that we utilise the same
OL,10,Fplatforms to inform migrants about the
OL,11,Ftruths about crossing the Channel and
OL,12,Fcoming to the UK illegally," they said
OL,13,Fin a statement.
OL,15,F"The relentless action we have taken
OL,16,Freduced crossings by 36% last year,
OL,17,Fwhich saw similar weather conditions
OL,18,Fto 2022."
