OL,6,FThe Times reported that a shortlist of
OL,7,Finfluencers has been drawn up in
OL,8,FAlbania with the help of a private
OL,9,Fmarket consultancy.
OL,11,FThe list includes a rapper, two
OL,12,Fcomedians, lifestyle bloggers, TV
OL,13,Fpersonalities and a travel writer.
OL,15,FThe Home Office has a budget of about
OL,16,F#30,000 to pay the Albanian
OL,17,Finfluencers, who have been chosen for
OL,18,Ftheir ability to appeal to young men.
OL,20,FCost would be capped at #5,000 per
OL,21,Fperson.
