OL,3,CHome Office to pay TikTok influencers
OL,4,Cto deter migrants from crossing Channel
OL,6,FMore than 1,000 migrants have arrived
OL,7,Fin the UK so far this year after
OL,8,Fcrossing the Channel.
OL,10,FTikTok, a video-sharing platform owned
OL,11,Fby Chinese company ByteDance, has
OL,12,Fboomed in popularity over recent
OL,13,Fyears, and is now estimated to have
OL,14,Fover one billion users.
OL,16,FThe scheme is designed to evade the
OL,17,Fban on government use of TikTok after
OL,18,Fsecurity concerns were raised
OL,19,Fsurrounding its privacy policy.
