OL,6,FIt means the Home Office, or any
OL,7,Fgovernment official, cannot advertise
OL,8,Fdirectly on the app.
OL,10,FThe process follows additional
OL,11,Fdeterrence campaigns that have been in
OL,12,Fthe works for three years with
OL,13,Factivity in Albania, France, and
OL,14,FBelgium, the Home Office said.
OL,16,FHome Office paid-for social media
OL,17,Factivity in Albania has already
OL,18,Freached over 946,000 people.
